<item>
            <title>[TIKA-228] Add OSGi metadata to Tika</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TIKA-228</link>
                <project id="12310631" key="TIKA">Tika</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The attached patch adds OSGi metadata to Tika Core. Of course, it will take some more effort to make the whole of Tika OSGi-compatible (parser plugins etc), but at this time I only need the MIME detection. Rather than repacking the JAR myself, I hope this will be seen as a useful first step.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
