                            <comment id="12712218" author="jukkaz" created="Fri, 22 May 2009 20:16:15 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Good idea. In fact I&apos;d like to enlarge the scope of this issue to cover OSGi metadata also for the tika-parsers and tika-app packages.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12712252" author="jukkaz" created="Fri, 22 May 2009 21:49:49 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve now applied the patch to tika-core and added simple OSGi metadata also to tika-parsers and tika-app.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m no OSGi expert so the metadata settings may still need some tweaking, but we can take care of any improvements in other more detailed issues. Resolving this issue as Fixed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
